Sample spring boot java application build using maven in jenkins docker container
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Date : 23-11-2020
Environment:jenkins server -->jenkinsci/blueocean docker container

Maven : Installed on docker automatically(maven 3.6.3v)

Java : Didn't select ,using the default java from the running docker container

Maven plugin :

git repo :https://github.com/rjshk013/jenkinslearning/

need to select branch as master

Tasks will run:
-----------------

1.Build will be done at folder in docker jenkins folder 

Building in workspace /var/jenkins_home/jobs/springboot1/workspace
2.Clone git repo already configured 
Cloning repository https://github.com/rjshk013/jenkinslearning/

3.Find pom.xml and download artifacts

4.Build done as per the given maven goal ,here clean package

5.It will create jar snapshot of Demo1Application.java project 
6.After successful build it will store jar file to location in docker 

Archiving /var/jenkins_home/jobs/springboot1/workspace/target/demo1-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar to com.example/demo1/0.0.1-SNAPSHOT/demo1-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar

Reference : https://thenucleargeeks.com/2020/03/26/building-a-spring-boot-application-in-jenkins/


